snippet.title: Petrified Pawns Demo Trailer (New content update)
snippet.description:
Wishlist on steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3210650/Petrified_Pawns/
You can play the demo for free on steam. Recently added new maps and a ton of new features such as faster movement and combat. New items and spells and new enemy units to fight against.
